headline: Curious about Agilent (A) Q2 Performance? Explore Wall Street Estimates for Key Metrics
summary: Looking beyond Wall Street's top -and-bottom-line estimate forecasts for Agilent (A), delve into some of its key metrics to gain a deeper insight into the company's potential performance for the quarter ended April 2025.
